creator: WeOpt
descriptionHtml:
Join the First Land Of Poker (FLOP) community, meet likeminded poker players, share with them about your Poker experience, and improve your game skills.

- Find likeminded Poker friends, engage, and share your experience and passion for poker.
- Share and LEARN from top Poker players anywhere at anytime.
- Stay aware about the latest NEWS about Poker in real time.
- Create your live Poker INTEREST LISTS(IL) in our #floppartner Poker rooms and invite your friends to join you at the table.
- Get an easy and fast access, in real time, to the RUNNING CASH GAMES and WAITING LISTS in our #floppartner Poker Rooms.
- TRACK your Poker CASH GAME SESSIONS in easy and fast way.
- Build your PLAYER PROFILE and share your preferences and results with your bakers and coaches.
- Create a secure One to One or Group private CHAT with your Poker friends.

By joining flop App, you will be able to find Live Poker Cash Games in our flop partner Casinos, Clubs, and Card Rooms, and register to the waiting lists without being physically in the Poker Room. More than this, flop App helps you to connect with like minded Poker players around your area, view their Player Profiles, and start together your Poker Cash Game in any flop partner Casino close by in two clics.
